  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624410/extras/e2504d617dbd5684296ad45878901d0b.poster.avif?t=1712556039\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624410/extras/e2504d617dbd5684296ad45878901d0b.webm?t=1712556039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624410/extras/e2504d617dbd5684296ad45878901d0b.mp4?t=1712556039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Zoom through levels at mach speeds!</h2>At its very core, <strong><i>SINGULARIUM</i></strong> is a game about speed. It's a Fast-Paced 3D platformer, that has you using the various movement mechanics to their fullest, such as wallrunning, bunny hopping, and your ability to create black holes that pull you around, to try to beat each level with a fast time. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624410/extras/4fc91c784e8cae11154062d0831c1f98.poster.avif?t=1712556039\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624410/extras/4fc91c784e8cae11154062d0831c1f98.webm?t=1712556039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624410/extras/4fc91c784e8cae11154062d0831c1f98.mp4?t=1712556039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Black Hole Physics</strong> - moving while being pulled will allow you to curve around your black hole, adding a ton of complexity and enriching the movement system for those skilled enough to master it.<br></li><li> <strong>Hardcore Gameplay</strong> - Quick reactions will be vital if you want to beat these levels while going at breakneck speeds!<br></li><li> <strong>Tons of Levels</strong> - SINGUALRIUM has 20+ handcrafted levels, with more to come!<br></li><li> <strong>In-game Leaderboards - compare your times with the best of the best!<br></strong></li><li> <strong>Level Editor</strong> - Create and share your own custom levels!<br></li><li> <strong>Complex Movement System</strong> - combining wallrunning, walljumping, swinging, and bunny hopping will allow you to zoom through the levels<br></li><li> <strong>Builtin Level Timers</strong> - Compare your level times with your friends!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624410/extras/d1141e53ceb1a7e0c622badb392783b0.poster.avif?t=1712556039\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624410/extras/d1141e53ceb1a7e0c622badb392783b0.webm?t=1712556039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2624410/extras/d1141e53ceb1a7e0c622badb392783b0.mp4?t=1712556039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
